* Prerequisite
1. Visual studio C# 2010 express edition - You can download it from following link 
http://www.microsoft.com/visualstudio/en-us/products/2010-editions/visual-csharp-express.

2. Hyves consumer key and secret - Please follow following steps for getting consumer key and secret
	a. Create Hyves Account - Create hyves account from following link http://www.hyves.nl/create/
	b. Create Hyves API Consumer - Create hyves consumer from following link http://www.hyves.nl/developer/apiconsumer/
		i.   Select Type as "Desktop"
		ii.  Fill in Name
		iii. Fill in Description
		iv.  Enter security tag from email, (You will get after clicking link next to this field)
		v.   Leave rest of the fields blank
	c. Consumer key and secret - Now you can get consumer key from application you just created from following link http://www.hyves.nl/developer/applications/


* How run project
1. Update consumer key and consumer secret in following file Hyves.Desktop.Interface\app.config 
2. Open HyvesFotos.sln with visual studio C# express edition and start debugging to run application




